[rousing music]

1:20:11.041 --> 1:20:12.541
[gunshots]

1:20:18.833 --> 1:20:19.875
[rapid gunfire]

1:20:26.125 --> 1:20:28.208
[intense musical build-up]

1:20:33.916 --> 1:20:35.833
-[gunshots]
-[tense music]

1:20:39.166 --> 1:20:41.000
