1:20:41.083 --> 1:20:43.250
[nephew] I have an army.

1:20:43.333 --> 1:20:45.541
Oh, yeah? Well, I've got my mom.

1:20:48.291 --> 1:20:49.500
[laughs]

1:20:49.583 --> 1:20:51.750
