1:20:53.875 --> 1:20:55.291
I wish we had more time, Ma.

1:20:56.375 --> 1:20:57.916
It's quality, not quantity.

1:21:01.208 --> 1:21:02.333
Chin up.

1:21:03.125 --> 1:21:06.291
