I'll shoot you in the stomach.

1:21:17.291 --> 1:21:19.000
Then we'll have some real fun together.

1:21:19.083 --> 1:21:20.791
[mouthing]

1:21:26.166 --> 1:21:27.541
[tense music]

1:21:29.250 --> 1:21:30.708
[Florence] Hey, dum-dums.

1:21:38.125 --> 1:21:39.541
[gunshots]

1:21:40.916 --> 1:21:43.666
[Anna May] Hey, idiots. Catch these.

1:21:50.875 --> 1:21:51.833
[metallic clang]

1:21:56.666 --> 1:21:58.416
[coughing]

1:22:04.208 --> 1:22:06.208
[birds and animals calling]

1:22:34.750 --> 1:22:36.375
[coughing]

1:22:38.208 --> 1:22:41.541
[nephew] Idiots to the left.
Morons to the right.

1:22:41.625 --> 1:22:44.750
The rest of you knuckleheads stay here
and kill those two.

1:22:46.500 --> 1:22:48.208
[chains rattle]

1:22:48.291 --> 1:22:50.125
[hammers swoosh]

1:22:55.291 --> 1:22:57.541
[tense music]

