1:38:43.500 --> 1:38:45.250
We had a deal.

1:38:45.333 --> 1:38:46.958
And I'm a man of my word.

1:38:48.166 --> 1:38:51.083
I will set the girl free, unharmed.

1:38:53.750 --> 1:38:56.250
