1:39:59.083 --> 1:40:00.833
It's no place for a kid.

1:40:00.916 --> 1:40:02.416
Stay out of this, ladies.

1:40:03.041 --> 1:40:04.125
It's not your fight.

1:40:05.166 --> 1:40:07.541
There's no more standing on the sidelines.

1:40:07.625 --> 1:40:09.541
We all need to pick a side.

1:40:09.625 --> 1:40:11.250
-Right, ladies.
